data.description: SPACIOUS 1-STORY HOME WITH RECENT GREAT UPDATES SUCH AS: AC '23, Roof '22, Furnace '22, Solar Panels, Water Softener PLUS ADDED BONUS Home is Covered under Choice Home Warranty (transfer to buyer at closing!!)!Open Floor Plan! Be greeted by gleaming hardwood floors cover private study with French Doors & Dining space next to Study for additional space to gather. Proceed to Great Room with spacious Kit featuring Center Island, Granite c-tops & SS app. Liv Rm has wall of windows to capture the sunlight & backyard view. Enjoy outdoors under the covered patio. Split bdrm- 2 bdrms & bath on one side while Primary Bdrm suite is nestled on opposite. A spacious sitting rm is connected to Primary Bdrm makes great 2nd office, Exercise Rm, Nursery or Sitting Room. Bath features Dual Sinks, Garden Tub, Separate Shower & Large WIC.  Little Elm ISD ALL STEM Curriculum Certified, Including the High School. *ASK AGENT TO SEE PAST ELECTRIC BILLS & THE SAVINGS  YOU WILL GET WITH THE SOLAR PANELS!*
